            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>1. Quality Issues</h2>
                <p>If you receive flowers that are damaged, wilted, or not as described, please contact us within 24 hours of delivery with photos of the issue. We will:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Offer a replacement delivery at no additional cost</li>
                    <li>Provide a full refund if replacement is not possible</li>
                    <li>Issue store credit for future purchases</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>2. Delivery Issues</h2>
                <p><strong>Late Delivery:</strong> While we strive for timely delivery, we cannot guarantee exact delivery times due to traffic and weather conditions. Late delivery alone does not qualify for a refund.</p>
                <p><strong>Failed Delivery:</strong> If we are unable to deliver due to incorrect address or recipient unavailability, we will attempt to contact you to reschedule. Additional delivery fees may apply.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>3. Order Cancellation</h2>
                <p><strong>Before Processing:</strong> Orders cancelled within 1 hour of placement receive a full refund.</p>
                <p><strong>After Processing:</strong> Orders already being prepared may be subject to a cancellation fee up to 50% of the order value.</p>
                <p><strong>Same-day Orders:</strong> Cannot be cancelled once processing has begun.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>4. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
                <p>The following are generally not eligible for refunds:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Custom arrangements and special orders</li>
                    <li>Event and wedding orders cancelled within 72 hours</li>
                    <li>Gift cards and promotional items</li>
                    <li>Delivery fees (unless delivery was our error)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>5. Refund Process</h2>
                <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Contact our customer service team within 24 hours of delivery</p>
                <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Provide order details and photos if applicable</p>
                <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> We will review your case within 48 hours</p>
                <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Approved refunds are processed to your original payment method</p>
                <p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> 5-7 business days for credit card refunds</p>
            </div>

            <div class="refund-section">
                <h2>6. Store Credit</h2>
                <p>In some cases, we may offer store credit instead of a monetary refund. Store credit:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Never expires</li>
                    <li>Can be used for any future purchase</li>
                    <li>Is transferable</li>
                    <li>Cannot be redeemed for cash</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

